course.subject: SCED
course.name: Advanced Studies in the Teaching and Learning of Biology
course.description: Addresses the laboratory skills, investigatory skills, and assessment skills of Biology education in the secondary school and provides an in-depth theoretical and practical framework for teaching and learning of biology.
course.prerequisites: SCED 4210 (prior to 2011-12) and SCED 4310 (prior to 2011-12)
